install 

www.baidu.com   search git_

download git 

$ sudo apt-get install git 


1: make an git project 

 1) cd your project 
 2) git config --global user.name " aaaaa "
    git config --global user.email "1231@qq.com"
    git init 
    
    ** move your project in this path 
    git add 1.py  (git add . )
    git commit -m "the first change"

2:update to github 
    1) in your Repository
    2) check new
    3) input repository name  and some description then check creat repository
    4)  cd your project and run 
	git remote add origin https://github.com/liuzhenhui/git__install_and_use.git
	(in the web  this shell will be given)
	git push -u origin master
    5) ok
